    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Tubular electric discharge lamps in which ionization of mercury vapor produces radiation that activates the fluorescent coating on the inner surface of the glass.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
